remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7004f-102">スマートラベルを有効にすると、ユーザー定義のルールのセットに基づいて、重複するデータポイントラベルがグラフで再配置されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-102">When smart labels are enabled, the chart repositions overlapping data point labels, based on a set of user-defined rules.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7004f-103">ラベルとそのデータポイントをリンクするために、引き出し線が描画されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-103">Callout lines will be drawn to link the label with its data point.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7004f-104">引き出し線の視覚属性を制御できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-104">The visual attributes of the callout line can be controlled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7004f-105">これらの視覚属性には、色、線のスタイル、および線の幅が含まれます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-105">These visual attributes include color, line style, and line width.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7004f-106">プロパティ<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A> と <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> プロパティは、引き出し線の端に表示される矢印などの embellishments を制御します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-106">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> properties control the embellishments, such as arrowheads, that appear at the end of the callout line.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7004f-107">プロパティは、任意<xref:System.Drawing.Color>のオブジェクトに設定できます。 <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-107">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A> property can be set to any <xref:System.Drawing.Color> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7004f-108">引き出し線の色を設定した場合は、の色<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A>と、 <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>で定義されている embellishment も自動的に設定されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-108">If you set the color of the callout line, you will also automatically set the color of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the embellishment defined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7004f-109">プロパティ<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A>は、引き出し線のピクセル幅を制御します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-109">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A> property controls the pixel width of the callout line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7004f-110">このプロパティを使用する<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>と、およびの embellishments もスケーリングされます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-110">Use of this property will also scale the embellishments of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7004f-111">スマートラベルの移動は、モーション関連のいくつかのプロパティを使用して制御できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-111">The movement of smart labels can be controlled through the use of several motion-related properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7004f-112">これらは、方向、距離、およびデータポイントラベルをプロットエリアから移動できるかどうかのルールを定義します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-112">These define the rules of movement for the direction, distance and whether the data point label is allowed to leave the plotting area.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7004f-113">既定の移動ルールでは、通常、ほとんどの問題が解決されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-113">The default movement rules will normally resolve most issues.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7004f-114">は<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> 、データポイントラベルが重なり合う場合に移動できる最大距離をピクセル単位で指定する値を定義します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-114">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> defines a value that specifies the maximum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels are allowed to be moved in case of overlapping.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7004f-115">プロパティ<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A>は、データポイントラベルが重なり合う場合に移動されるデータポイントからの最小距離をピクセル単位で指定する値を定義します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-115">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> property defines a value that specifies the minimum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels will be moved in case of overlapping.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7004f-116">データポイントラベルの位置を再設定する必要がある場合、ラベルは少なくとも指定されたピクセル数だけ移動します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-116">When a data point label needs to be repositioned, the label will be moved by at least the number of pixels specified.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7004f-117">プロパティ<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A>は、重複する問題を解決できない場合にラベルを非表示にするかどうかを示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-117">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property indicates whether the labels are hidden when overlapping issues cannot be resolved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7004f-118"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A> <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A>プロパティが`true`であり、で指定された領域内にデータポイントを描画できない場合、データポイントラベルは描画されません。 <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-118">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property is `true`, and the data point cannot be drawn within the area specified by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> in the directions allowed by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>, the data point label will not be drawn.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7004f-119">プロパティ<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>は、データポイントラベルを移動できる方向を定義します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-119">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A> property defines the direction(s) in which the data point label can be moved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7004f-120">このプロパティは、 <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> 1 つの値、または複数<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>の値のビットごとの or を受け取ります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-120">This property accepts one <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> value or a bitwise-OR of multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7004f-121">既定値は、すべて<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>の値のビットごとの or で、データポイントの中心を除くすべての可能な方向での再配置を可能にします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-121">The default is the bitwise-OR of all <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values, to allow repositioning in all possible directions except to the center of the data point.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7004f-122">スマートラベルは、次の種類のグラフではサポートされていません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-122">Smart labels are not supported for the following chart types:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="7004f-123">横棒グラフ: 横棒グラフと 100% 積み上げ横棒グラフ。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-123">Bar charts: bar and hundred-percent-stacked bar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="7004f-124">図形グラフ: 円グラフ、ドーナツグラフ、極座標グラフ、およびレーダーチャート。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-124">Shape charts: pie, doughnut, polar and radar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="7004f-125">範囲グラフ: 範囲、範囲列、範囲横棒グラフ。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-125">Range charts: range, range column and range bar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="7004f-126">積み上げ面グラフ: 積み上げ面グラフと 100% 積み上げ面グラフ。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7004f-126">Stacked area charts: stacked area and hundred-percent-stacked area charts.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```vb  
Imports System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
Private Function SetSmartLabelsOptions()  
  
   ' Enabling the SmartLabels™ attribute.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.Enabled = true  
  
   ' Set the callout style.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutStyle = LabelCalloutStyle.Underlined  
  
   ' Set the callout line color.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineColor = Color.Goldenrod;  
  
   ' Set the callout line style.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineStyle = ChartDashStyle.Dash  
  
   ' Set the callout line width.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineWidth = 3   
  
   ' Set the callout line anchor cap.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineAnchorCap = LineAnchorCap.Arrow  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
using System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
private void SetSmartLabelsOptions()  
{  
   // Enabling the SmartLabels™ attribute.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.Enabled = true;  
  
   // Set the callout style.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutStyle = LabelCalloutStyle.Underlined;  
  
   // Set the callout line color.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineColor = Color.Goldenrod;  
  
   // Set the callout line style.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineStyle = ChartDashStyle.Dash;  
  
   // Set the callout line width.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineWidth = 3;  
  
   // Set the callout line anchor cap.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineAnchorCap = LineAnchorCap.Arrow;  
}  
```
